<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Bitdefender GravityZone | Lacchia Tecnologia</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; }
        .glass { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-[#050b1a] text-white antialiased">

    <nav class="container mx-auto px-6 py-8 flex justify-between items-center">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-blue-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center font-bold">LT</div>
            <span class="text-xl font-bold">Lacchia <span class="text-blue-500 text-[20px]">Tecnologia</span></span>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="container mx-auto px-6 pt-12 pb-24 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div>
            <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1 rounded-full bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/20 text-blue-400 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">
                Parceiro Oficial Bitdefender
            </div>
            <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-extrabold leading-tight mb-8">
                Prote&ccedil;&atilde;o total contra <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-cyan-300">Ataques Digitais.</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg mb-10 leading-relaxed">
                O Bitdefender GravityZone oferece seguran&ccedil;a multicamadas contra Ransomware e Malware. A solu&ccedil;&atilde;o ideal para a Lacchia Tecnologia proteger o seu negócio.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass p-8 md:p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-2xl">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Or&ccedil;amento Gratuito</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-400 mb-8 text-sm italic">Receba um diagn&oacute;stico hoje mesmo.</p>
            
            <form action="#" class="space-y-5">
                <input type="text" placeholder="Seu Nome" class="w-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-4 text-white outline-none focus:border-blue-500">
                <input type="email" placeholder="E-mail Corporativo" class="w-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-4 text-white outline-none focus:border-blue-500">
                <button class="w-full bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold py-5 rounded-2xl hover:bg-blue-500 transition shadow-lg shadow-blue-600/20 uppercase tracking-widest text-sm">
                    Garantir Prote&ccedil;&atilde;o
                </button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="container mx-auto px-6 py-12 border-t border-white/5 text-center text-gray-500 text-xs">
        &copy; 2026 Lacchia Tecnologia. Todos os direitos reservados.
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
